sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Endpoint
    participant Mediator
    participant Handler
    participant Encryption
    participant Domain as N8NConfiguration
    participant N8N as n8n API
    participant DB as Database
    participant Events

    Client->>Endpoint: POST /api/v1/admin/workflows/n8n/{id}/test

    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Extract configId
    Endpoint->>Endpoint: Create TestN8nConnectionCommand

    Endpoint->>Mediator: Send(command)

    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(command)

    Handler->>DB: Get N8NConfiguration
    DB-->>Handler: Configuration

    Handler->>Encryption: DecryptApiKey(encryptedKey)
    Encryption-->>Handler: Decrypted API key

    Handler->>N8N: GET /healthz
    Note over Handler: Headers: X-N8N-API-KEY

    alt Connection successful
        N8N-->>Handler: 200 OK {version: "0.220.0"}

        Handler->>Domain: RecordTestResult(true, "Connected to n8n v0.220.0")
        Domain->>Domain: LastTestedAt = UtcNow
        Domain->>Domain: LastTestResult = success message
        Domain->>Events: Raise N8NConfigurationTestedEvent

        Handler->>DB: SaveAsync(configuration)
        DB-->>Handler: Saved ✓

        Handler-->>Mediator: {success: true, message: "Connected"}
    else Connection failed
        N8N-->>Handler: Error (timeout/401/500)

        Handler->>Domain: RecordTestResult(false, errorMessage)
        Domain->>Domain: LastTestedAt = UtcNow
        Domain->>Domain: LastTestResult = error message

        Handler->>DB: SaveAsync(configuration)

        Handler-->>Mediator: {success: false, message: errorMessage}
    end

    Mediator-->>Endpoint: TestResult

    Endpoint-->>Client: 200 OK
    Note left of Client: {success, message, testedAt}
